The Shocking Truth of Amber Heard vs Johnny Depp Revealed
Subscribe To InformOverload: http://bit.ly/2xB5CqA
Recent Uploads: https://bit.ly/32ACSiM

Johnny Depp and Amber Heard have been involved in a handful of lawsuits dating back to their divorce in 2017. By that point, Heard had accused Depp of abuse, and that would lead to an April 2018 headline by The Sun, which referred to Depp as a Wife Beater. Recently, Judge Andrew Nicol determined that Amber’s claims were substantial, which also let The Sun off the hook. The 14 incidents that lead to the judge’s ultimate decision, which include the 12 leading to the court’s ultimate decision, as well as what he thought regarding each specific incident have now been released.
